📊 Daily Expense Tracker

A simple and efficient web-based application to track daily income and expenses. This project helps users manage their personal finances by recording transactions and monitoring overall balance.

✨ Features
➕ Add income and expense entries
🗂️ Categorize transactions (Food, Travel, Shopping, etc.)
💰 View total balance, income, and expenses
🧾 Easy-to-use interface
📱 Lightweight and fast performance
🎯 Objective

The main goal of this project is to help users track their daily spending habits and improve financial management skills while practicing web development concepts.

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML
CSS
JavaScript (update if you used other languages like Python/Java)
🚀 How to Run the Project

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/shivarajadharshini/daily-expense-tracker.git
Open the project folder
Run index.html in your browser
            📈 Future Improvements
Add database support (MySQL / Firebase)
